column5: we fished out of dunkrik got our limit 12 eye's we got 1 off a rigger and 11 off dipsy's. 55ft down on the rigger and 150ft and 180ft on the dipsy's all fish were cought with wormharness.
Wow! You're certainly batting a thousand on Erie. Congrats!
thats some great fishing !!! got any fish porn to show of that adventure???

Nice haul...  That open water trolling looks fun... Figuring out the art of trolling suspended walleye...  All my fishing is on shallow structure....12-25 feet of water...  Lots of spots and lots of short trolls in a day...
thanks Roy  sorry fishindevil forgot the camera but 7 were over 8lb one 28in laker and a 16in silver perch  thanks mike if you find them its great if not it can be a long day
